title: Amir Reza Nasr Azadani
text:
Amir Nasr Azadani (, born February 7, 1996) is an Iranian <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who last played for Iranian club <a href="Tractor%20S.C.">Tractor</a> in the <a href="Persian%20Gulf%20Pro%20League">Persian Gulf Pro League</a>.
Club career.
Nasr Azadani joined <a href="Rah%20Ahan%20F.C.">Rah Ahan</a> in 2015, after spending his youth career at <a href="Sepahan%20F.C.">Sepahan</a>.
